version_description: There are no published chord versions of this song, so I decided to create one. This version can be played right along with the recording created by the artist.
This is a simple version with power chords in standard tuning suitable for beginners and folks who want to keep it easy at the campfire.

song_name: Ive Got You Under My Skin

version_description: This is my first tab on this website. Hope you like it. I'm always open to suggestions so if you have something to say just do it.
If your new, a C/G chord is a C chord but your adding in the sixth string 3rd fret. It gives the C chord more bass. Playing a regular C chord is fine.
A good version for a single acoustic guitar.
